<p>▲沈光宇作品欣赏</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p3.itc.cn/images01/20200810/bb1a4c1ca049442cbebb7ab1387ed3bc.png" max-width="600" /></p>
<p>▲沈光宇作品欣赏</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p9.itc.cn/images01/20200810/e2320de779094d85b326af8825b4651b.png" max-width="600" /></p>
<p>▲沈光宇作品欣赏</p>